{"type":"text","timestamp":1781763553426,"sessionID":"ses_126a03146ffe6yn9ha3tk3Qb0n","part":{"id":"prt_ed9621f05001KzQn2y6JdCj4R0","messageID":"msg_ed961fbdb001k0VK3jzERUKhEC","sessionID":"ses_126a03146ffe6yn9ha3tk3Qb0n","type":"text","text":"A concrete candidate is emerging in retention sweep with `SPECKIT_SOFT_DELETE_TOMBSTONES=true`: the candidate predicate appears to require `deleted_at IS NOT NULL`, which excludes live expired rows. I’m checking tests/docs before classifying severity.","time":{"start":1781763546885,"end":1781763553422},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0942dbcf7e41749f016a338ddad9208191ba0fb2f3c0b86fba","phase":"commentary"}}}}
