{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781763837127,"sessionID":"ses_126a03146ffe6yn9ha3tk3Qb0n","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_eaJ4JzeV4uiNX2G3utdklPSa","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-review/scripts/tests/fixtures/blocked-stop-session/review/iterations/iteration-001.md","offset":1,"limit":180},"output":"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-review/scripts/tests/fixtures/blocked-stop-session/review/iterations/iteration-001.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Iteration 1: Correctness baseline for reducer state transitions\n2: \n3: ## Focus\n4: Correctness review of reducer fixture state transitions and registry bookkeeping.\n5: \n6: ## Findings\n7: ### P1 - Required\n8: - **F003**: Missing null guard in registry merge - `src/registry.ts:88` - Correctness path dereferences prior state before checking the record exists.\n9: \n10: ### P2 - Suggestion\n11: - **F002**: Stale stop-gate snapshot reuse - `src/gates.ts:64` - Correctness fallback can replay outdated gate state when later iterations update the review snapshot.\n12: \n13: ## Ruled Out\n14: - Dashboard rendering bug in the progress table was not reproducible from the traced inputs.\n15: \n16: ## Dead Ends\n17: - Replaying the same correctness trace with synthetic durations did not change the registry outcome.\n18: \n19: ## Recommended Next Focus\n20: Expand into security review around export and reducer boundary handling to verify whether any active path can escalate beyond correctness-only impact.\n\n(End of file - total 20 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Iteration 1: Correctness baseline for reducer state transitions\n\n## Focus\nCorrectness review of reducer fixture state transitions and registry bookkeeping.\n\n## Findings\n### P1 - Required\n- **F003**: Missing null guard in registry merge - `src/registry.ts:88` - Correctness path dereferences prior state before checking the record exists.\n\n### P2 - Suggestion\n- **F002**: Stale stop-gate snapshot reuse - `src/gates.ts:64` - Correctness fallback can replay outdated gate state when later iterations update the review snapshot.\n\n## Ruled Out\n- Dashboard rendering bug in the progress table was not reproducible from the traced inputs.\n\n## Dead Ends\n- Replaying the same correctness trace with synthetic durations did not change the registry outcome.\n\n## Recommended Next Focus\nExpand into security review around export and reducer boundary handling to verify whether any active path can escalate beyond correctness-only impact.","truncated":false,"loaded":[],"display":{"type":"file","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-review/scripts/tests/fixtures/blocked-stop-session/review/iterations/iteration-001.md","text":"# Iteration 1: Correctness baseline for reducer state transitions\n\n## Focus\nCorrectness review of reducer fixture state transitions and registry bookkeeping.\n\n## Findings\n### P1 - Required\n- **F003**: Missing null guard in registry merge - `src/registry.ts:88` - Correctness path dereferences prior state before checking the record exists.\n\n### P2 - Suggestion\n- **F002**: Stale stop-gate snapshot reuse - `src/gates.ts:64` - Correctness fallback can replay outdated gate state when later iterations update the review snapshot.\n\n## Ruled Out\n- Dashboard rendering bug in the progress table was not reproducible from the traced inputs.\n\n## Dead Ends\n- Replaying the same correctness trace with synthetic durations did not change the registry outcome.\n\n## Recommended Next Focus\nExpand into security review around export and reducer boundary handling to verify whether any active path can escalate beyond correctness-only impact.","lineStart":1,"lineEnd":20,"totalLines":20,"truncated":false}},"title":".opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-review/scripts/tests/fixtures/blocked-stop-session/review/iterations/iteration-001.md","time":{"start":1781763837118,"end":1781763837126}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0260b45fe1d5f35c016a338efcf8e8819185d14078fb3dcaff"}},"id":"prt_ed9668cb8001uTvOj6yCQzPYgK","sessionID":"ses_126a03146ffe6yn9ha3tk3Qb0n","messageID":"msg_ed9666776001FHCvZnDnbTPFUC"}}
